ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisReappointment of MICHAEL SAUNDERS of Ottawa, Ontario, as Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective April 3, 2019.
